opinion.court: Supreme Court of the United States

opinion:
FCC, ET AL.
v.
CBS CORP., ET AL.

No. 08-653

Supreme Court of United States.

May 4, 2009.

The petition for writ of certiorari is granted. The judgment is vacated and the case is remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit for further consideration in light of FCC v. Fox Television Stations, Inc., 556 U.S. ___ (2009).
